    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叫上好友，开始摇滚！打开《超弦乐队》，拿上 VR 设备，和朋友们组建 4 人梦幻乐队。调好乐器，登上舞台，化身吉他大神、贝斯达人、鼓手狂魔或键盘高手，用音浪燃爆全场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/cd7ca06a6beaec3efd6c7ee5a5a12540.poster.avif?t=1733129833\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/cd7ca06a6beaec3efd6c7ee5a5a12540.webm?t=1733129833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/cd7ca06a6beaec3efd6c7ee5a5a12540.mp4?t=1733129833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滑动击打音符，跟随鼓点尽情演奏，用炫酷键盘指法征服所有人。与队友在 5 大舞台上演奏曲目，挑战各种音乐风格，还可以通过单人模式进行练习。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/49e6d12b7112222aa0a025ae952df063.poster.avif?t=1733129833\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/49e6d12b7112222aa0a025ae952df063.webm?t=1733129833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/49e6d12b7112222aa0a025ae952df063.mp4?t=1733129833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为吉他、架子鼓、贝斯和键盘大师</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《超弦乐队》集结了摇滚乐队的灵魂乐器。拿起吉他，来一段震撼独奏，也可以用虚拟架子鼓稳住节奏。每首歌曲都为不同乐器量身定制乐谱，无论你选择哪种乐器，都能获得出众体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人独奏或多人合奏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《超弦乐队》率先在 VR 音乐游戏中提供完整的乐队体验，让你能够和朋友们在线组队完成歌曲。更喜欢单人独奏也没问题，每首歌的各个乐器部分都可以由你独自完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内置曲库，支持 Mod.io</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《超弦乐队》不仅自带涵盖流行曲目和独立音乐的歌曲库，但你也可以利用 Mod.io 平台，在单人模式中找到并导入心中金曲到游戏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/e2fd7e896710a3cd3013a1b15347013f.poster.avif?t=1733129833\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/e2fd7e896710a3cd3013a1b15347013f.webm?t=1733129833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182070/extras/e2fd7e896710a3cd3013a1b15347013f.mp4?t=1733129833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
